    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Json's internal encoder fails to encode the solidus (<a href="http://www.json.org/">http://www.json.org/</a> and <a href="http://www.json.org/string.gif">http://www.json.org/string.gif</a>) when attempting to encode strings.  This could potentially result a potential security risk when transfering un-escaped and unsafe HTML to a json client who's primary intention is to display it in the browser.</p>

